         <abstract>
            <p>A collocation procedure for efficient integration of rapidly oscillatory functions is presented. The integration problem is transformed into a certain O.D.E. problem, and this is solved by a collocation technique. The method is also extended to two-dimensional integration, and some numerical results are appended showing the efficiency of the method in handling difficult cases of rapid irregular oscillations.</p>
          </abstract>
